Logical Programs on static
1. What is the output of the program?
public class Test1
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        int x = 20;
        System.out.println("Main method: " + x);
    }

    static
    {
        int x = 10;
        System.out.println("Static block: " + x);
    }
}

✅ Output
Static block: 10
Main method: 20



